--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.2.1 (2020-02-21)
E: Update root.hints file (2020022000)

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-09-27)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.1.1 (2019-09-18)
E: Utilize 'validate' parameter

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.3 (2018-12-18)
E: Minor Jinja2 style improvement

* Version 1.0.2 (2018-12-13)
E: Ensure port is set by default

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-12)
E: Minor Jinja2 style improvement

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-09-03)
F: Add support for 'include' option (unbound_include)

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-08-22)
F: Initial release
